Subject: [PATCH 06/16] media: cadence: csi2rx: Soft reset the streams before starting capture
Date:   Tue, 30 Mar 2021 23:03:38 +0530
Message-ID: <20210330173348.30135-7-p.yadav@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.0
